1^2 \cdot 2! + 2^2 \cdot 3! + \cdots + n^2 \cdot (n+1)! =\sum_{k=1}^{n} k^2 \cdot (k+1)!
f_k = (k-1) (k+2)!
f_k-f_{k-1} = k^2 (k+1)!
\begin{align}\sum_{k=1}^n k^2 (k+1)! &= f_1 - f_0 + f_2 - f_1 + \ldots+f_{n}-f_{n-1}\\ &= f_n-f_0\\  &= (n-1)(n+2)! + 2\end{align}
